data.description: 4BR/2.5BA Brick Front Traditional Two-Story in a Highly Sought After Hillgrove HS District Nestled Back on half Acre Private Wooded Lot.  Great Location Close to West Cobb Shopping and Dining! Two Story Entry Foyer, Formal French Door Study/Home Office with Bay Window, Separate Dining Room with Hardwood Floors, Bay Window and French Doors, Fireside Family Room with Fireplace, Bright Open Kitchen with Island Bar, White Cabinets, Stainless Appliances, Gas Range, and Eat-in Kitchen, Powder Room, and Two Car Garage Complete the Main Floor.  Upstairs includes a Large Owners Suite with Sitting Room, Double Vanity, Garden Tub, Separate Shower, Walk-in Closet and Additional Closet, Three Additional Guest Bedrooms with a Full Guest Bathroom, and upstairs Laundry.  Private Backyard with Expanded Patio with Stone Walkway and Storage Shed. Updated HVAC, Small Neighborhood with No HOA*** 100% Financing and First Time Buyer Grant Money Available *** If buyer closes loan with preferred lender, Mark Baker/SWBC Mortgage, lender will provide one-year temporary rate buydown (1% below current market rate) at no cost to buyer.)
